Frequently Asked Questions

How do I place an order?

Simply register or login, enter your train and seat details, browse our menu, add items to cart, and checkout. Your food will be delivered to your seat within 30-45 minutes.

What payment methods do you accept?

We accept cash on delivery, mobile banking (bKash, Nagad, Rocket), and credit/debit cards.

Can I cancel my order?

Yes, you can cancel your order within 5 minutes of placing it. After that, the food preparation begins and cancellation may not be possible.

Is there a minimum order amount?

No, there is no minimum order amount. However, a delivery fee of ‡ß≥50 applies to all orders.
